        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig 10 A and B show typical examples of immuno-EM against Septin 6 in mouse cerebellum (10A) and olfactory bulb (10B). DAB precipitate is only detected in presynaptic terminals. No quantification is offered.. Experimental description: M&M: \"We used preembedding immunoperoxidase and immunogold labeling methods. Mouse brains were fixed with PB\"" ;
